dreisoft.tresos.guidedconfig.api.gui.xform

Class WidgetModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • dreisoft.tresos.guidedconfig.api.gui.xform.WidgetModelElement
      • dreisoft.tresos.guidedconfig.api.gui.xform.WidgetModel

  • public class WidgetModel
extends WidgetModelElement
    A WidgetModel describes the parameters needed to instantiate a single widget.

    The WidgetModel is normally fead from an XML model describing the parameters for each widget to show.

    Parameters that are needed to instantiate the widget are added as sub elements of type WidgetModelElement to this class.

    The value of the WidgetModel is an empty string.
